8_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1535\">هذا البند يشمل الأضرار في المولدات ومصادر الطاقة</span></div><input type=\"text\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/note16\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"\" id=\"id1536\"></label><label class=\"question non-select \"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1537\">(في حال إضافة أكثر من بند قم بالضغط على إشارة (+) بالأسفل)</span></div><input type=\"text\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/note17\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"\" id=\"id1538\"></label><fieldset class=\"question simple-select  type-singleChoice\"><fieldset><legend><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1539\">3.18.1 مصدر الطاقة</span><span class=\"required\" id=\"id1540\">*</span>\n                    </legend><div class=\"option-wrapper\"><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/Q3_18_1_energy_source\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/Q3_18_1_energy_source\" value=\"1\" data-required=\" /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/IS_Current_Location ='1' and  /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/General_Information/Applicant_Information/Q1_8_survey_status  = '2'\" data-type-xml=\"select1\" id=\"id1541\">\n      <i class=\"webfor