of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/Q3_18_13_Power_Source_Photos\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1616\">(في حال إضافة أكثر من صورة قم بالضغط على إشارة (+) بالأسفل)</span></div><input type=\"text\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/Q3_18_13_Power_Source_Photos/note18\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"\" id=\"id1617\"></label><fieldset class=\"question simple-select  type-singleChoice\"><fieldset><legend><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1618\">يرجى رفع صور واضحة وقت حدوث الضرر، في حال توافرها.</span>\n                    </legend><div class=\"option-wrapper\"><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/Q3_18_13_Power_Source_Photos/Q3_Power_Source_photos\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/Q3_18_13_Power_Source_Photos/Q3_Power_Source_photos\" value=\"1\" data-type-xml=\"select1\" id=\"id1619\">\n      <i class=\"webform-svg-icon radio\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <g>\n    <path class=\"background\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 0c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12S0 18.627 0 12 5.373 0 12 0zm0 3a9 9 0 100 18 9 9 0 000-18z\"></path>\n    <path class=\"checkmark\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 6a6 6 0 110 12 6 6 0 010-12z\"></path>\n  </g>\n</svg></i>\n    <span lang=\"\" class=\"option-label active\" id=\"id1620\">صورة الموقع قبل الضرر</span></label><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/Q3_18_13_Power_Source_Photos/Q3_Power_Source_photos\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/Q3_18_13_Power_Source_Photos/Q3_Power_Source_photos\" value=\"2\" data-type-xml=\"select1\" id=\"id1621\">\n      <i class=\"webform-svg-icon radio\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <g>\n    <path class=\"background\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 0c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12S0 18.627 0 12 5.373 0 12 0zm0 3a9 9 0 100 18 9 9 0 000-18z\"></path>\n    <path class=\"checkmark\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 6a6 6 0 110 12 6 6 0 010-12z\"></path>\n  </g>\n</svg></i>\n    <span lang=\"\" class=\"option-label active\" id=\"id1622\">صورة الموقع بعد الضرر</span></label></div></fieldset></fieldset><label class=\"question non-select or-appearance-\"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1623\">قم بإضافة صورة للمصدر الطاقة المذكور</span></div><input type=\"file\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/Q3_18_13_Power_Source_Photos/Q3_18_13_1_Power_Source_Before_Damage\" data-type-xml=\"binary\" accept=\"application/*\" id=\"id1624\"></label><label class=\"question non-select or-appearance-hidden\"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1625\">قم بإضافة صورة للمصدر الطاقة المذكور بعد الضرر.</span></div><input type=\"file\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/Q3_18_13_Power_Source_Photos/Q3_18_13_1_Power_Source_After_Damage\" data-type-xml=\"binary\" accept=\"application/*\" id=\"id1626\"></label>\n            </section><div class=\"or-repeat-info\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources/Q3_18_13_Power_Source_Photos\"></div>\n            </section><!--end of group -->\n            </section><div class=\"or-repeat-info\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_18_Damages_to_Generators_and_Power_Sources\"></div>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group \" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components\"><h4><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1627\">3.19 الأضرار في المكونات اللوجستية ومكونات الدعم</span></h4><section class=\"or-repeat \" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1628\">في هذا البند، يرجى إضافة جميع الأضرار التي لحقت بالمكونات اللوجستية ومكونات الدعم الخاصة بالجهة أو الموقع، بما في ذلك أي مكونات لم يتم ذكرها سابقًا في الطلب. يشمل ذلك على سبيل المثال لا الحصر: المكاتب الإدارية، المعدات المكتبية، أجهزة الاتصالات، المعدات التكنولوجية، وأي عناصر داعمة أخرى ضرورية لاستمرار العمل الإداري واللوجستي.</span></div><input type=\"text\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/note20\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"\" id=\"id1629\"></label><label class=\"question non-select \"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1630\">(في حال اضافة أكثر من بند قم بالضغط على اشارة (+) بالأعلى)</span></div><input type=\"text\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/note21\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"\" id=\"id1631\"></label><label class=\"question non-select \"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1632\">3.19.1 الوصف</span><span class=\"required\" id=\"id1633\">*</span></div><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\" id=\"id1634\">مثال: أثاث مكتب الادارة وما يتضمنه من معدات مكتبية وأجهزة كهربائية وأجهزة مكيفات وحواسيب وطابعات يتم إدخالها في بند واحد مع إجمال التقدير في الأسفل</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_1_description\" data-required=\" /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/IS_Current_Location ='1' and  /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/General_Information/Applicant_Information/Q1_8_survey_status  = '2'\" data-type-xml=\"string\" id=\"id1635\"><span class=\"or-required-msg active\" lang=\"\" id=\"id1635\" data-i18n=\"constraint.required\">This field is required</span></label><fieldset class=\"question simple-select  type-singleChoice\"><fieldset><legend><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1636\">3.19.2 حالة الضرر</span><span class=\"required\" id=\"id1637\">*</span>\n                    </legend><div class=\"option-wrapper\"><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_2_damage_status\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_2_damage_status\" value=\"1\" data-required=\" /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/IS_Current_Location ='1' and  /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/General_Information/Applicant_Information/Q1_8_survey_status  = '2'\" data-type-xml=\"select1\" id=\"id1638\">\n      <i class=\"webform-svg-icon radio\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <g>\n    <path class=\"background\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 0c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12S0 18.627 0 12 5.373 0 12 0zm0 3a9 9 0 100 18 9 9 0 000-18z\"></path>\n    <path class=\"checkmark\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 6a6 6 0 110 12 6 6 0 010-12z\"></path>\n  </g>\n</svg></i>\n    <span lang=\"\" class=\"option-label active\" id=\"id1639\">كلي (تضرر كامل أدى إلى دمار أو فقدان الوظيفة بشكل تام)</span></label><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_2_damage_status\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_2_damage_status\" value=\"2\" data-required=\" /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/IS_Current_Location ='1' and  /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/General_Information/Applicant_Information/Q1_8_survey_status  = '2'\" data-type-xml=\"select1\" id=\"id1640\">\n      <i class=\"webform-svg-icon radio\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <g>\