al_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_4_Logistics_Support_Photos\"><h4><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1662\">3.19.4 صور المكونات اللوجستية ومكونات الدعم</span></h4><section class=\"or-repeat \" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_4_Logistics_Support_Photos\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1663\">(في حال إضافة أكثر من صورة قم بالضغط على إشارة (+) بالأعلى)</span></div><input type=\"text\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_4_Logistics_Support_Photos/note22\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"\" id=\"id1664\"></label><fieldset class=\"question simple-select  type-singleChoice\"><fieldset><legend><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1665\">يرجى رفع صور واضحة وقت حدوث الضرر، في حال توافرها.</span>\n                    </legend><div class=\"option-wrapper\"><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_4_Logistics_Support_Photos/Q3_Logistics_Support_photos\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_4_Logistics_Support_Photos/Q3_Logistics_Support_photos\" value=\"1\" data-type-xml=\"select1\" id=\"id1666\">\n      <i class=\"webform-svg-icon radio\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <g>\n    <path class=\"background\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 0c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12S0 18.627 0 12 5.373 0 12 0zm0 3a9 9 0 100 18 9 9 0 000-18z\"></path>\n    <path class=\"checkmark\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 6a6 6 0 110 12 6 6 0 010-12z\"></path>\n  </g>\n</svg></i>\n    <span lang=\"\" class=\"option-label active\" id=\"id1667\">صورة الموقع قبل الضرر</span></label><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_4_Logistics_Support_Photos/Q3_Logistics_Support_photos\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_4_Logistics_Support_Photos/Q3_Logistics_Support_photos\" value=\"2\" data-type-xml=\"select1\" id=\"id1668\">\n      <i class=\"webform-svg-icon radio\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <g>\n    <path class=\"background\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 0c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12S0 18.627 0 12 5.373 0 12 0zm0 3a9 9 0 100 18 9 9 0 000-18z\"></path>\n    <path class=\"checkmark\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 6a6 6 0 110 12 6 6 0 010-12z\"></path>\n  </g>\n</svg></i>\n    <span lang=\"\" class=\"option-label active\" id=\"id1669\">صورة الموقع بعد الضرر</span></label></div></fieldset></fieldset><label class=\"question non-select or-appearance-\"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1670\">قم بإضافة صور للمكونات اللوجستية ومكونات الدعم</span></div><input type=\"file\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_4_Logistics_Support_Photos/Q3_19_4_1_Logistics_Support_Before_Damage\" data-type-xml=\"binary\" accept=\"application/*\" id=\"id1671\"></label><label class=\"question non-select or-appearance-hidden\"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1672\">قم بإضافة صور للمكونات اللوجستية ومكونات الدعم بعد الضرر.</span></div><input type=\"file\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_4_Logistics_Support_Photos/Q3_19_5_1_Logistics_Support_After_Damage\" data-type-xml=\"binary\" accept=\"application/*\" id=\"id1673\"></label>\n            </section><div class=\"or-repeat-info\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components/Q3_19_4_Logistics_Support_Photos\"></div>\n            </section><!--end of group -->\n            </section><div class=\"or-repeat-info\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification/Q3_19_Damages_to_Logistics_and_Support_Components\"></div>\n            </section><!--end of group -->\n            </section><div class=\"or-repeat-info\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Damages_Facilities_Components/Location_Identification\"></div>\n            </section><!--end of group -->\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group \" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Q4_Damages_Vehicles_Engineering_Euipment\"><h4><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1674\">رابعا : أضرار المركبات والمعدات الهندسية</span></h4><section class=\"or-repeat or-appearance-field-list\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Q4_Damages_Vehicles_Engineering_Euipment\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1675\">في هذا البند، يرجى إدخال جميع المركبات والمعدات الهندسية المتضررة أو المستخدمة في الموقع. ويشمل ذلك كل مركبة أو معدة وجميع الملحقات أو الأدوات المرتبطة بها، مثل المعدات الميكانيكية الإضافية، الأدوات الخاصة بالرفع أو الحفر، أو أي ملحقات تشغيل أخرى. الهدف من ذلك هو توثيق كل المركبات والمعدات لتسهيل عمليات الصيانة، الإصلاح، أو الاستبدال وتقدير الأضرار بشكل دقيق.</span></div><input type=\"text\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Q4_Damages_Vehicles_Engineering_Euipment/note24\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"\" id=\"id1676\"></label><label class=\"question non-select \"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1677\">(في حال إضافة أكثر من بند قم بالضغط على إشارة (+) بالأعلى)</span></div><input type=\"text\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Q4_Damages_Vehicles_Engineering_Euipment/note25\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"\" id=\"id1678\"></label><label class=\"question non-select  type-number\"><div class=\"label-container\"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1679\">4.1 رقم المركبة</span><span class=\"required\" id=\"id1680\">*</span></div><div class=\"widget number\"><input type=\"number\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Q4_Damages_Vehicles_Engineering_Euipment/Q4_1_vehicle_number\" data-required=\" /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/General_Information/Applicant_Information/Q1_8_survey_status  = '2'\" data-constraint=\"regex(., '^[0-9]{7}$')\" data-type-xml=\"int\" id=\"id1681\"><i class=\"webform-svg-icon\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M9.56973 8.22652C9.60928 8.42988 9.62906 8.64681 9.62906 8.87729C9.62906 9.31923 9.56088 9.70945 9.42454 10.048C9.2882 10.3865 9.10719 10.6897 8.88152 10.9577C8.65585 11.2257 8.39727 11.4678 8.10578 11.6841C7.81429 11.9003 7.5134 12.107