كانت المركبة مشمولة مع معدة هندسية مثل الثلاجات المحمولة يتم وصف ذلك هنا.</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Q4_Damages_Vehicles_Engineering_Euipment/Q4_2_vehicle_description\" data-required=\" /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/General_Information/Applicant_Information/Q1_8_survey_status  = '2'\" data-type-xml=\"string\" id=\"id1686\"><span class=\"or-required-msg active\" lang=\"\" id=\"id1686\" data-i18n=\"constraint.required\">This field is required</span></label><fieldset class=\"question simple-select  type-singleChoice\"><fieldset><legend><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1687\">4.3 حالة الضرر</span><span class=\"required\" id=\"id1688\">*</span>\n                    </legend><div class=\"option-wrapper\"><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Q4_Damages_Vehicles_Engineering_Euipment/Q4_3_damage_status\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Q4_Damages_Vehicles_Engineering_Euipment/Q4_3_damage_status\" value=\"1\" data-required=\" /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/intro/platform_detect ='web'\" data-type-xml=\"select1\" id=\"id1689\">\n      <i class=\"webform-svg-icon radio\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <g>\n    <path class=\"background\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 0c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12S0 18.627 0 12 5.373 0 12 0zm0 3a9 9 0 100 18 9 9 0 000-18z\"></path>\n    <path class=\"checkmark\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 6a6 6 0 110 12 6 6 0 010-12z\"></path>\n  </g>\n</svg></i>\n    <span lang=\"\" class=\"option-label active\" id=\"id1690\">كلي (تضرر كامل أدى إلى دمار أو فقدان الوظيفة بشكل تام)</span></label><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/Q4_Damages_Vehicles_Engineering_Euipment/Q4_3_damage