  <i class=\"webform-svg-icon radio\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <g>\n    <path class=\"background\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 0c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12S0 18.627 0 12 5.373 0 12 0zm0 3a9 9 0 100 18 9 9 0 000-18z\"></path>\n    <path class=\"checkmark\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 6a6 6 0 110 12 6 6 0 010-12z\"></path>\n  </g>\n</svg></i>\n    <span lang=\"\" class=\"option-label active\" id=\"id1823\">نعم</span></label><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/G_Return_to_Work/Q7_2_rubble_obstacle_to_work\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/G_Return_to_Work/Q7_2_rubble_obstacle_to_work\" value=\"2\" data-required=\" /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/General_Information/Applicant_Information/Q1_8_survey_status  = '2'\" data-type-xml=\"select1\" id=\"id1824\">\n      <i class=\"webform-svg-icon radio\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <g>\n    <path class=\"background\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 0c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12S0 18.627 0 12 5.373 0 12 0zm0 3a9 9 0 100 18 9 9 0 000-18z\"></path>\n    <path class=\"checkmark\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 6a6 6 0 110 12 6 6 0 010-12z\"></path>\n  </g>\n</svg></i>\n    <span lang=\"\" class=\"option-label active\" id=\"id1825\">لا</span></label></div></fieldset><span class=\"or-required-msg active\" lang=\"\" id=\"id1826\" data-i18n=\"constraint.required\">This field is required</span></fieldset><fieldset class=\"question simple-select  type-singleChoice\"><fieldset><legend><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\" id=\"id1827\">7.3 هل بالإمكان الانتقال إلى المناطق الصناعية عند توفر الإمكانية لاستئناف النشاط؟</span><span class=\"required\" id=\"id1828\">*</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\" id=\"id1829\">هذا السؤال يهدف لمعرفة إمكانية استئناف العمل في الموقع الحالي أو نقل النشاط مستقبلاً إلى مناطق صناعية، في حال كانت هناك إمكانيات مناسبة للنقل والتشغيل، مع مراعاة البنية التحتية والتراخيص اللازمة.</span>\n                    </legend><div class=\"option-wrapper\"><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/G_Return_to_Work/Q7_3_relocation_to_industrial_zones\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/G_Return_to_Work/Q7_3_relocation_to_industrial_zones\" value=\"1\" data-required=\" /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/General_Information/Applicant_Information/Q1_8_survey_status  = '2'\" data-type-xml=\"select1\" id=\"id1830\">\n      <i class=\"webform-svg-icon radio\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <g>\n    <path class=\"background\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 0c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12S0 18.627 0 12 5.373 0 12 0zm0 3a9 9 0 100 18 9 9 0 000-18z\"></path>\n    <path class=\"checkmark\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 6a6 6 0 110 12 6 6 0 010-12z\"></path>\n  </g>\n</svg></i>\n    <span lang=\"\" class=\"option-label active\" id=\"id1831\">نعم</span></label><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/G_Return_to_Work/Q7_3_relocation_to_industrial_zones\" data-name=\"/IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/G_Return_to_Work/Q7_3_relocation_to_industrial_zones\" value=\"2\" data-required=\" /IND_Damage_Assessment_of_Damaged_Industrial_Facilities/General_Information/Applicant_Information/Q1_8_survey_status  = '2'\" data-type-xml=\"select1\" id=\"id1832\">\n      <i class=\"webform-svg-icon radio\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <g>\n    <path class=\"background\" fill=\"#000\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 0c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12s-5.373 12-12 12S0 18.627 0 12 5.373 0 12 0zm0 3a9 